<paragraph id="11EA63A3B82817EE8C1260193CE4D7A4" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Material examined.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="897D0D75773EE894CA1039FB34CD0393" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">NHM_446 NHMUK 20170073.1-2, collected 2013-10-20, 13.86367 -116.54432, 4050 m. http://data.nhm.ac.uk/object/d69b581d-8a79-4c4d-8f70-88b2ec07d86e</paragraph>
